schools.name: Dr. Walter C. Ralston Intermediate School

data.description: Welcome to this classic ranch house that is a true HOME.  A place where children can be in the Garden Grove Unified school district and they can enjoy lush large green backyard filled with beautiful plumeria trees, fruit trees and take a splash in the pool.   Located in the center part of Garden Grove this home has four bedrooms, two baths, formal living room featuring stone covered fireplace, dinning area and a kitchen.  Covered / handicap accessible patio with an attached bonus second kitchen make it a wonderful home for family gatherings. Close to freeways, shopping center & Southern California attractions.  With little TLC this can become the HOME of your dreams.
